73-90cc-951bf1385c58.png\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Deck 3 Plan</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/24/bbff972d-a270-4920-b0fc-1196b09b8724.png\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Deck 4 &nbsp;Plan</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/24/adf0fa91-517b-43d4-8acd-932c34c20c0d.png\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;font-size:16px;background-color:#00D5FF;\"><strong>房间介绍</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<i><span style=\"color:#CC33E5;font-size:14px;\"><strong>360度豪华套房</strong></span></i> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<i><span style=\"color:#CC33E5;\"><strong><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/24/9ba3382b-e5d3-4346-a055-7476b6c390fd.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong></span></i> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-align:center;margin-left:0pt;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/24/f5ccc25c-ccd8-4118-bb18-39e05a426311.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-align:center;margin-left:0pt;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/24/0a4bb6b3-b8af-41c4-a906-44d5b91a4a4d.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-align:center;margin-left:0pt;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/24/4f551c95-8711-4cf7-a827-7d4567df3c6c.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-align:center;margin-left:0pt;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/24/8ebd2d60-18a7-4f9d-9488-8be8f30a1f52.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#00D5FF;\"><strong>潜水路线</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">本次路线为马尔代夫最经典的中部环礁路线，我们会先后经过南北马累环礁、南北阿里环礁、斐郦都</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;color:#666666;\">环礁。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-align:center;margin-left:0pt;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/24/2ade88d1-ce25-4db9-aab3-3c5efdc770e8.png\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/24/2135d6a9-cf42-44d3-a70c-f984cae0812b.png\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">在这条路线上，我们将会看到鲸鲨、manta、鲨鱼群、鹰鳐群、护士鲨群。大片美丽珊瑚、五颜六色</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;color:#666666;\">的鱼群将令你流连忘返。在潜水休息的时间，我们还会安排海钓、浮潜、无人岛私人派对，BBQ，海</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;color:#666666;\">鲜大餐以及原始自然岛屿参观等丰富的活动。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/24/7bab6579-f161-44cd-91a2-290b857d63f4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/24/cd2bcae3-f7cb-4369-9e62-598147cecd33.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/24/66bda9aa-289b-455d-9d4d-f253da622214.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#00D5FF;\"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#00D5FF;\"><strong>推荐航班</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#337FE5;font-size:14px;\">去程</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">： &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">9月25日 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">浦东T1（12:45)----马累(17:40) &nbsp;&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#666666;\">上海航空FM843 &nbsp; &nbsp;</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#337FE5;font-size:14px;\">返程</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;\">：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">10月2日</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">马累机场（18:40）----浦东T1（05:35）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">上海航空FM844</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#B8D100;font-size:14px;\"><strong>小贴士</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#B8D100;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">&nbsp;随身携带好护照、签证、信用卡、机票等出国（境）旅游身份</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">证明及相关凭据，妥善保管。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#B8D100;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">要严格遵守有关国际公约和出境游目的地国家（地区）的入境</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">法规，不得携带违禁药品，不得参与</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">目的地国家（地 &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">区）禁止</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">从事的活动。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#B8D100;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">出境期间不要携带大量现金和贵重物品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#B8D100;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">熟悉所在国的交通信号标志，遵守其交通规则。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#B8D100;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">尊重当地风俗习惯（马尔代夫全民信奉伊斯兰教）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#B8D100;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">游艇的甲板为唯一的可吸烟区域，其余各处禁止吸烟</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#B8D100;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">带小孩的游客请随时照看好自己的小孩。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#B8D100;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">根据自身身体状况，自备感冒等药品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#B8D100;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">带好防晒用品，保护皮肤。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#B8D100;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">爱护海洋，不带垃圾下海，不破坏海底生物。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#B8D100;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">饮酒后切勿游泳、浮潜及潜水。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#B8D100;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">乘坐船、快艇等水上交通工具时，要穿救生衣（圈）等。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#B8D100;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">浮潜必须结伴而行，切勿一人独自下海。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#B8D100;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">潜水员需携带潜水执照，并在潜水行程制定之前出示给潜导确认。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#B8D100;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">潜水前耐心听潜导对本次潜水水域的介绍以及潜伴划分，仔细</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">阅</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">读潜水风险责任书，并签署免责申</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;color:#666666;\">明。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#B8D100;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">潜水时应严格控制上升速度，严格遵守5米3分钟安全停留制度。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#B8D100;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#666666;\"> 船宿下海潜水要求：OW及以上</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-align:center;margin-left:0pt;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/24/659d8c67-5f03-4350-9fa6-0679148f81ae.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/24/782529ee-eec7-4193-9288-adcf67c5bf98.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/24/66a18eed-e6c3-4d33-aa07-f444a074bdb4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:left;margin-left:0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#337FE5;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:15px;\">☆ 感兴趣的小伙伴们欢迎来询/潜程小秘书“童童”（微信号：boyes127 或电话：18001661552)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-align:center;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#CC33E5;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">|</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\"></span></span><i><span style=\"color:#CC33E5;\"><br />\r\n</span></i></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-align:center;\">\r\n	<b><i> <span style=\"color:#CC33E5;\">邂逅</span></i></b><b><i>&nbsp;• <span style=\"color:#FF9900;\">Maldives</span></i></b> \r\n</p>');
INSERT INTO `dive_activity` VALUES ('d7228d55-6fe7-4ec9-9ac7-87cecae21fbe', '2016-03-07 11:19:39', '', '阿尼洛', '2016-07-01', '【OW初级考证行程】•阿尼洛站', '上海', '2016-05-27', null, 'AT02', '1fc35d88-2a75-44ec-9e6c-8ade2f5f941e', null, null, null, null, '', '', null, '0', 'uploadfiles/activity/activity_EYD01457321112580.jpg', '<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<em><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">【OW初级考证行程】</span>•<span style=\"color:#9933E5;\">阿尼洛站</span></span></strong></em><em><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#9933E5;\"></span></strong></em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#E56600;\"><em>＆</em></span><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/03/29/4ee22675-6f39-4bd5-8b6e-c36a2c845d38.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><em><span style=\"color:#E56600;font-size:16px;\">【阿尼洛的美】</span></em></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">Anilao小镇安静恬然，宛若世外桃源，风光独特的海岸线延28公里，并且拥有世界级的海底风景与生</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;color:#666666;\">态环境。这里是菲律宾水肺潜水的发源地，并且有着“微距天堂”和“世界海兔之都”的美誉。因为世界</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;color:#666666;\">上绝大部份的海兔在这里都能找到。潜水胜地40个，常年吸引着来自世界各地来的潜水员。Anilao是</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;color:#666666;\">中国潜水员的最爱，它水流温和，海底生态丰富多样，能见度一般在二十米以上，适水合水摄爱好者</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;color:#666666;\">及潜水新手。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/03/29/b28d292c-6c9f-488f-aa8a-a62501f2e363.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/03/29/7d01d5f2-bf5e-4bbc-ba85-90d14604287a.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<em><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#E56600;\">About Pier Uno \r\nResort宇野码头潜水度假村</span></strong></em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-indent:0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\">宇野码头潜水度假村是一家星级酒店，可让您的八打雁之行变得更完美。酒店拥有高品质的服务以及</span><span style=\"color:#666666;font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:10.5pt;line-height:1.5;\">完善的设施，可满足游客们的所有需求。无线网络（公共区域）, 吸烟吸烟区, 货币兑换, 家庭</span><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\">房,</span><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\">&nbsp;接送服务等设施都已配备，可供住客使用。客房内饰优雅，便捷设施齐全。酒店环境宁静，还设</span><span style=\"color:#666666;font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:10.5pt;line-height:1.5;\">有游泳池（儿童）, 按摩浴缸,水上</span><span style=\"color:#666666;font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\">运动项目（非机动项目）, 私人海滩, 钓鱼等休闲设施。下榻宇野</span><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">码头潜水度假村，可方便您前往八打雁各区!度假村还配有其它</span><b><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">特色服务</span></b><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">:酒吧、卡拉OK厅、室内游泳</span><span style=\"color:#666666;font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\">池、餐厅室外游泳池、按摩保健、私人海滩趴等！让您的潜水旅行更完美！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-indent:0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:9pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;background-color:white;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/03/29/a28d8512-2b86-4fd3-8aa6-8536b70b49f1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/03/29/0d12d6a4-6d13-45ef-b766-727e2fbcdf5e.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#E56600;\">行程安排：5天4晚（5月27日—5月31日 /2016年）</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#666666;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#666666;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">•&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">26日：收拾行李，整装待发。浦东机场集合，搭乘27日凌晨飞机由上海抵达马尼拉。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;•&nbsp;27日上午休息释放身心，感受Pier uno度假村的异国风情，中午开始学习潜水的理论课，泳池实习。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#666666;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#666666;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">•&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">28日-30日：出海，与大海亲密接触感受潜水的乐趣。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#666666;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#666666;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">•&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">31日：白天自由活动，晚上飞机回上海。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/03/29/1fac8e99-2298-4eb2-8b70-0da1ca36c03d.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';color:#E56600;font-size:12pt;\"><em>行程费用</em></span></b><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#DFC5A4;font-size:14px;\">（海景双人房）&nbsp; 俩人一间</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"text-indent:0pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<b><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">△</span></b><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">价格: 4820元/位，（单人需补房差，4晚房差一共：1350元）</span><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:9pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;\">\r\n	<b><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">△</span></b><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">&nbsp;另OW考证：3000（RMB）（证书、教程、教练培训）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/03/29/a4d49916-4e05-4560-95e5-758d3e866d57.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><em><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#E56600;\">费用包含</span></em></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-indent:0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">★机场到度假中心的来回接送</span><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:9pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-indent:0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">★6次船潜，含气瓶，配重，船费及潜导</span><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:9pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-indent:0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">★餐厅区域免费WiFi&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:9pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-indent:0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">★4晚所选房型住宿，两人一间</span><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:9pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-indent:0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">★一日三餐（Café牛奶热可可无限畅饮）</span><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:9pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-indent:0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">★无限岸潜(8:00-17:00)</span><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:9pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/03/29/b1a586b8-88b8-4e61-bd73-569aa8142d83.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;\">\r\n	<span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';color:#E56600;font-size:12pt;\">费用不包含</span><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:9pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-indent:0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\">★所有机票费用不包含</span><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:9pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-indent:0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\">★海岸公园及保育费每人每天约5美金</span><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:9pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-indent:0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\">★小费，每人约10美金（5天）</span><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:9pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-indent:0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\">★装备租赁费用 （25美元/人/天）</span><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:9pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-indent:0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\">★酒精和软饮料</span><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';font-size:9pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-indent:0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\';color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\">★菲律宾签证费用</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-indent:0pt;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/03/29/4a9d688f-9026-4a4b-8602-c0ca93908097.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/03/29/6af483fd-3c37-4013-9807-1202b19db6c5.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"color:#337FE5;\">★</span><span style=\"color:#337FE5;\"></span><span style=\"color:#337FE5;\">感兴趣的童鞋们欢迎咨询【潜程】小秘书：boyes127 \r\n微信 或致电：18001661552！</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	|\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><em><span style=\"color:#60D978;\"> 遇 &nbsp;见</span> &nbsp;</em></strong><strong></strong><strong>• <span style=\"color:#FF9900;\">&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#FF9900;\">Anilao</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>');
INSERT INTO `dive_activity` VALUES ('d7656280-c0ee-4be1-b5df-b55ba79ef9ba', '2016-05-16 09:58:42', '梦开始的地方·巴厘', '巴厘  蓝梦岛', '2016-08-04', '【梦开始的地方】巴厘 · 蓝梦岛', '上海', '2016-07-31', null, 'AT01', '1fc35d88-2a75-44ec-9e6c-8ade2f5f941e', null, null, null, null, '', '', null, '5', 'uploadfiles/activity/activity_DNYb1463363922360.jpg', '<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:10px;\"><em><strong><span style=\"background-color:#60D978;\"></span><span style=\"color:#003399;font-size:18px;\">【梦开始的地方】巴厘</span></strong></em></span><span style=\"color:#003399;font-size:18px;\"><em><strong>·蓝梦岛</strong></em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#337FE5;font-size:18px;\"><strong><em><span style=\"color:#FFE500;\">＆</span></em><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:10px;\"><em><strong> &nbsp; &nbsp; </strong></em></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">景物绮丽，风情万种，这是巴厘岛的真实写照。喜欢旅游的你一定知道巴厘！</span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<img class=\"\" src=\"http://img.xiumi.us/xmi/ua/tKLw/i/d3d07ea5edfb2edbbdc6dc4350d49ace-sz_108629.jpg@1l_640w.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#666666;\">然而，在巴厘以东，有一颗遗落在印度洋中的珍珠，它就是蓝梦岛！蓝梦岛，位于巴厘岛东南边的离岛，坐船三十分钟即可到达。这里的海水清澈无比，水下生物清晰可见，拥有海洋萌兽翻车鱼和魔鬼鱼，还有全东南亚最五彩斑斓的珊瑚礁，因此也被称为“玻璃海”。岛上居民多以种植海藻为生，因此也是巴厘岛的海藻养殖基地。在这里，你可以拥抱一个蓝色夏天的梦</span>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img class=\"\" src=\"http://img.xiumi.us/xmi/ua/tKLw/i/d45fc66c081add8b102fca1e5431d9c3-sz_148656.jpg@1l_640w.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">蓝梦岛遗世独立，碧海蓝天。在这梦幻一般的岛屿，海天一色，有巴厘岛最漂亮的海洋和沙滩，你可以抱着冲浪板冲进碧海蓝天里；也可以从海边悬崖上纵身而跃，身临其境与海浪来一场勇敢者的较量，享受驰骋在海浪上的快感；还可以可以潜水、骑行环岛，在山顶俯瞰玻璃海，探秘红树林，最后再邂逅一场美妙绝伦的海边日落。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img class=\"\" src=\"http://img.xiumi.us/xmi/ua/tKLw/i/253f7518ce8d2c577f715b06033a5596-sz_209680.jpg@1l_640w.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img class=\"\" src=\"http://img.xiumi.us/xmi/ua/tKLw/i/9ffc07da9655f6c3b2f15d06f9d008fc-sz_138800.jpg@1l_640w.jpg\" style=\"width:100%;\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img class=\"\" src=\"http://img.xiumi.us/xmi/ua/tKLw/i/c88f09cf8a6c7fc1cc7a07f2fc5fcf85-sz_434200.jpg@1l_640w.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#666666;\">蓝梦岛一共有16个潜点，分布在蓝梦岛的四周，其中最著名的是</span><span style=\"color:#E53333;\">Manta Cove/Bay（Manta 2潜点）</span>和<span style=\"color:#E53333;\">Crystal Bay<span style=\"color:#E53333;\">（水晶湾</span></span><span style=\"color:#E53333;\">）</span>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">Manta2潜点所在的海湾，是<span style=\"color:#E53333;\">魔鬼鱼</span>常去的清洁站，水下平静少有水流。在这里潜水，遇见魔鬼鱼的几率高达90％。如果运气爆棚还有机会看到蓝点鳐鱼、大理石鳐、竹鲨和护士鲨。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/16/8d190c87-65d1-4793-86af-355962d40c7f.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">水晶湾的名字因为蓝梦岛特有的<span style=\"color:#E53333;\">Mola mola(翻车鱼)</span>而尽人皆知，每年4月到10月份，来自世界各地的潜水客蜂拥而至蓝梦岛，为了一睹海洋萌兽翻车鱼的风采。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img class=\"\" src=\"http://img.xiumi.us/xmi/ua/tKLw/i/9e08565de0574dc9102fd67248ed731e-sz_21059.jpg@1l_640w.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">7、8月是巴厘岛一年中最好的时候。这两个月湿度比较低，太阳也不会过度炽热，海风吹起微微的凉意让人的身心都十分爽快。因此，潜程特地为小伙伴们推出一次巴厘游！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#3E3E3E;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#FFFFFF;font-size:16px;background-color:#999999;\"><strong>行程安排:</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#FFFFFF;font-size:16px;background-color:#999999;\"><strong>5天4晚(</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#FFFFFF;font-size:16px;background-color:#999999;\"><strong>7月31日-8月4日,6人成行）</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#00D5FF;font-size:14px;\">7月31日（周日）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">上海浦东机场飞往巴厘努拉莱伊机场（吉隆坡中转），由专车送往沙努尔码头，乘船前往蓝梦岛（船程30分钟），并入住休息</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#00D5FF;font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">8月1日（周一）</span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">上午两次潜水，下午一次潜水</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#00D5FF;font-size:14px;\">8月2日（周二）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">上午两次潜水，下午一次潜水</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#00D5FF;font-size:14px;\">8月3日（周三）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">上午两次潜水，下午一次潜水</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#00D5FF;font-size:14px;\">8月4日（周四）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">上午自由活动，下午前往巴厘努拉莱伊机场，返回国内。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#3E3E3E;font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"></span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#FFFFFF;font-size:16px;background-color:#999999;\"><strong>行程价格</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#CC33E5;font-size:14px;\"><strong><em>潜水员：4200元/人</em></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#CC33E5;font-size:14px;\"><strong><em><strong><em>非潜水员：2980元/人</em></strong><br />\r\n</em></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#1AF2ED;font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">费用包含：</span><em></em></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12.0000pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">9次潜水</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12.0000pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">巴厘岛到蓝梦岛往返船票及市内区域酒店接送（包含机场）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">酒店标准海景房（俩人一间）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">每天早餐和午餐</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">全天无限量巴厘咖啡和红茶</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">出海潜水包括潜水船、气瓶、配重带和配重，潜导</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">船上饮用水和小吃</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#CC33E5;font-size:14px;\"><em>OW考证学员：潜水员价格上另加2480元/人（6680元/人）</em></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#00D5FF;font-size:12px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#00D5FF;font-size:14px;\">费用不包含：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">机票（可代买）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">签证（可代办）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">旅行保险（可代买）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">岛上</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">的交通费（个人岛上额外费用）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">所有晚餐不包含</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">额外的潜水（40美金/潜）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">潜水装备租赁（全套装备含电脑表21美金/人·天）</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">小费及其他个人消费（建议每人每天2-3美金）</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12.0000pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">◆</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">单人入住需补房差800元/晚</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#888888;font-size:12px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-align:center;margin-left:0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Black\';color:#888888;font-size:14px;\"> <span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:#00D5FF;font-size:16px;\"><strong>Lembognan Dream Dive Resort</strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">蓝梦潜水度假村是一群热爱海洋，热爱生活的潜水教练来到蓝梦岛这个世外小岛，为这片“玻璃海”驻足停留然后决定用心经营的一家潜水度假村。度假村内配套齐全，包含中西各式早餐，24小时空调，热水，内设免费wifi，露天泳池 ，酒吧，全天免费提供咖啡和红茶。同时，蓝梦目前是唯一一家全中文教学运营的潜水度假村，提供全方位中文教学以及系统而专业的潜水培训，让你的潜水旅行安全而又舒适。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#3E3E3E;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/16/d76bd695-7bd6-444f-aaa6-2ec9052de9d7.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">潜水度假村坐落于蓝梦岛的核心海滩 JungutBatu，地理位置优越，可爱的弧形白沙滩与清澈碧蓝的海水构成一幅令人陶醉的画卷，你可以远眺巴厘岛上的阿贡火山，同时还欣赏到美丽的海湾景色与唯美日落。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#3E3E3E;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/16/f4e18587-c142-4e02-a185-a40d85cec7ed.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#D7ABA9;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/16/c69e26b4-b97d-4317-aba7-01cf140fa0d4.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#D7ABA9;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/16/60951de1-7031-4b36-815f-a284954c43c0.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-align:center;margin-left:0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#D7ABA9;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 萨努尔码头---蓝梦岛 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#3E3E3E;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><b><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#797BAA;\">（行船时刻表）</span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-align:center;margin-left:0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#D7ABA9;\">8:30 &nbsp; &nbsp; 11:00 &nbsp; &nbsp; 15:00</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#D7ABA9;font-size:12px;\">蓝梦岛---萨努尔码头</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\';color:#D7ABA9;font-size:12px;\">9:30 &nbsp; 13:00 &nbsp; &