olor:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">交通信息：</span></b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"></span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">巴厘岛下飞机前往沙努尔码头（车程1.5小时）、然后乘坐游轮到达蓝梦小岛（船程：30分钟）</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">教授语言</span></b><span style=\"color:#999999;\"></span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span></b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"></span><span style=\"color:#999999;\"></span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">中文、</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">英语</span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\"> \r\n<hr />\r\n</span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:36px;color:#999999;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong>其它信息</strong></span></span><span style=\"line-height:36px;color:#999999;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong></strong><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">蓝梦潜水度假村是一群热爱海洋，热爱生活的潜水教练来到蓝梦岛这个世外小岛，为这片“玻璃海”驻足停留然后决</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">定用</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">心经营的一家潜水度假村。度假村内配套齐全，包含中西各式早餐，</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">24</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">小时空调，热水，内设免费</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">wifi</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">，露天泳</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">池</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"> </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">，</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">酒吧，全天免费提供咖啡和红茶。同时，蓝梦目前是唯一一家全中文教学运营的潜水度假村，提供全方位中文教</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">学以及系统而专业的潜水培训，让你的潜水旅行安全而又舒适。潜水度假村坐落于蓝梦岛的核心海滩</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\"> JungutBatu</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">，地</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">理位</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">置优越，可爱的弧形白沙滩与清澈碧蓝的海水构成一幅令人陶醉的画卷，你可以远眺巴厘岛上的阿贡火山，同时</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\">还欣赏到美丽的海湾景色与唯美日落！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/02/c7af9549-eee6-4981-b32f-a6179f2c07b4.png\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/02/4ffcb205-674b-48df-a110-59c5b1df9e99.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/02/e4d0324e-16a1-49cc-b3d1-63fc8ed94d85.png\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/02/627be265-7a00-42d0-8d4f-