span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<span><strong><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\">星级</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">：7</span></span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">星</span><span></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#333333;line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;\">交通信息</span><span>：</span></span></b><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">度假村距</span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">马累机场</span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">分钟</span></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">船程(或水上飞机）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:\'sans serif\';color:#64451D;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\">教授语言</span></strong><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">英语、中文</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#333333;line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\"><strong>其它信息</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong>：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\"></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">索尼娃福斯位于马尔代夫Baa环礁的Kunfunadhoo岛，独立拥有这座热带私人岛屿，是马尔代夫第一家“鲁滨逊·克鲁索”传奇式风格的度假之所。55幢别墅零落地分布在沙滩边,隐藏在郁郁葱葱的树林里，环境相当私密。白色的沙滩轻轻的被蔚蓝的海水包围着，索尼娃芙西看上去就像标志性的鲁滨逊漂流记的场景，自然呈现低调的、智慧的奢华。索尼娃芙西低调奢华的感觉体现在它的客人的休闲着装和自然的建筑设计理念，却保留着豪华和充满幻想的本质。每栋别墅的面积都在235平米以上，空间非常宽敞，最适合举家入住。丰富的活动让父母和孩子都能在这里获得满满的欢乐和能量，无论是亲近大海或是拥抱绿色，享受阳光或是仰望星空。趣味无穷的儿童俱乐部给孩子们带来无与伦比的快乐时光，电影院、图书馆、音乐室、乐高玩具房等等让孩子们一天玩不够！</span> \r\n<hr />\r\n</span> \r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/488708e9-2c43-4524-a5cb-5c79ebdd2a3e.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/bb0cd7f9-a316-4d6a-986a-9c6be0dd2e00.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/f34b3095-9fa3-41f2-b225-291e0caf3206.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/fa56aaca-2fe9-43dc-8d43-67bfb738788c.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/93f44213-02c4-4f0a-88f7-82476dba51f6.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/359bb139-d7d5-43be-b473-0a783323e37e.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/161fd052-3f3e-4865-a210-939e988f9dc3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/cd970a5c-8219-477e-8830-65bfc7c9e29f.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/aa51fc86-ae7d-4afd-9d46-32d08fce625b.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/780553c8-ff03-4919-9847-b3b4473fa547.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span 