;color:#64451D;\">1923年</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">星级：</span></b></b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">5</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">星</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">交通信息</span></strong><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12.6px;line-height:18.9px;\">酒店距加里奥国际机场20英里（约40分钟车程）</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">教授语言</span></b><span style=\"color:#999999;\"></span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span></b><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">英语、中文</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\"> \r\n<hr />\r\n</span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:36px;color:#999999;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong>其它信息</strong></span></span><span style=\"line-height:36px;color:#999999;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong></strong><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:Helvetica;font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;\">☆坐拥全里约最壮丽的海景，科帕卡巴纳宫廷酒店自 1923 年开业起便成为了里约热内卢的地标。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:Helvetica;font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;\">酒店采用建筑外观照明方法，从而使它在夜晚也能像白天一样光鲜亮丽。它著名的 Art Deco 装饰派艺术大门、精致且个性化的风格以及绚丽的科帕卡巴纳海滨吸引着全世界顶级的明星与名流。酒店保留了一份自1920年代起长长的“金色名单“，名单上的客人均是耳熟能详的名字，从皇族到电影明星到音乐明星到政商界大佬应有尽有：滚石乐队、米克杰格、曼德拉、贾斯汀•比伯、查尔斯王子和戴安娜王妃、奥斯卡影后玛琳.黛德丽，还有法国总统萨科齐与其夫人布鲁尼等等。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:Helvetica;\">☆</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:Helvetica;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:Helvetica;color:#64451D;\">科帕卡巴宫廷酒店拥有全市最大且最迷人的泳池。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:Helvetica;color:#64451D;\">紧邻华丽的泳池畔的是超级酷的巴西风情酒吧 bar do copa，里约的时尚名流们最喜欢聚集在这里享受阳光浴，你可以在此欣赏丽人美景，也不要错过留心欣赏其独特的设计风格。酒店的餐厅也同样大受欢迎，不论是为了经高超技巧烹制而成的高档当地风味，或是厨师细心调配的精致意大利料理，热爱美食的你绝不会感到失望。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:Helvetica;font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;\">☆</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:Helvetica;font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;\"></span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:Helvetica;font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;\"></span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:Helvetica;font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;\">这是一座典雅的欧洲地中海风格与激情的南美风格完美结合的建筑经典。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-indent:0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;font-size:12px;font-weight:normal;line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"> \r\n	<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;color:#64451D;font-size:9pt;\">▽<br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;color:#64451D;font-size:9pt;\">上帝的杰作，里约夜色中的明珠！</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/d89c6b33-861f-4f1b-82d3-a38cd86fd296.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/84183116-7c31-4235-8971-c012d0c281ce.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/3e01d2cd-1fb1-4f09-8d55-2eaf7d34d10c.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/34a95466-de70-4e8f-a70c-0f13c27dca1d.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/81162df3-bb28-49e0-9ac6-5bf341e200e4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/01a0b568-6705-4cc7-9c54-7989afb18569.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/df6e7657-7f8b-47e6-ae72-8d6e875fc02c.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/cb5be9ba-f808-4225-a66f-5064980b393e.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/4ea98f5f-4f32-40fd-96e0-e35889643f8b.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/d8f81c46-e88a-4234-85de-e5941613158b.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/03dc501c-1626-4e84-b432-e217f80615f2.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/2f5cbe45-9be3-4fdd-ba96-4a6a97cbba9b.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>', '01768d64-6c80-4f7c-84dc-ce3b26064a1c', '0');
