 />\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">星级</span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">：<span style=\"color:#64451D;\">4</span></span></b></b><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">星</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">交通信息：</span></b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"></span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">度假村距离机场2小时</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<b><b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">教授语言</span></b><span style=\"color:#999999;\"></span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span></b><span style=\"color:#999999;\"></span><span style=\"color:#999999;\"></span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">英语、中文\r\n<hr />\r\n</span></span><span style=\"line-height:36px;color:#999999;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong>其它信息：</strong></span></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">EL Pinoy Dive&amp;Leisure Resort是一家坐落在海滩边上拥有</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">4</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">星等级的潜水度假村，位于著名的亚尼洛区，地理位置便</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">捷。 酒店内设多种设施和服务，可让您尽受舒适与酣睡。 酒店内设施繁多，礼宾接待服务</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">, </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">家庭房</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">, </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">餐厅</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">, </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">代客泊车</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">, </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">咖</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">啡店等都已配备。 部分客房内设 房内保险箱</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">, </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"