an style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">Diverhotel Tenerife Spa &amp; Garden旅馆提供配备了卫星电视和迷你吧的明亮的空调客房。每间客房均设有一个设备齐全的浴室。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">旅馆的El Drago自助餐厅供应各种地中海美食。旅馆还有一个池畔酒吧，可俯瞰旅馆迷人的场地。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">Spa一个水疗按摩浴缸和桑拿浴室以及包括按摩在内的各类护理服务。旅馆内还设有健身房。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">Puerto de la Cruz的中心距离旅馆约有5分钟步行路程；旅馆距离一个高尔夫球场仅有2公里。令人印象深刻的泰德山公园（Mount Teide Park）距离Diverhotel Tenerife Spa &amp; Garden旅馆约有15公里。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/19/868d4f96-62ee-4385-bd55-d3e8adb85428.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/19/068b72a8-45d5-4ad4-a331-39da6ca69788.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/19/2feae2b6-02f1-46bb-afc1-11abe7e630e1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/19/6a4c7dd6-6c12-4716-8c07-72fa118c29bf.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/19/c3d4753b-3e09-45a3-9d6b-adc217974f6a.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/2a873a0b-87ff-4d78-9e0f-626331121db8.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/19/7ffb2b2b-ace3-4ee4-be49-b89ec04e94e3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/32b36cb1-d1ef-4b4e-b00a-eb0d8f9c0a3e.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/afece191-ca27-4f13-af1d-4942c08078cd.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r