;font-family:NSimSun;\">交通信息：</span></b><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">距奥克兰市中心40分钟车程（直升飞机10分钟可到达）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">教授语言</span></b><span style=\"color:#999999;\"></span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span></b><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">英语、中文</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\"> \r\n<hr />\r\n</span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:36px;color:#999999;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong>其它信息</strong></span></span><span style=\"line-height:36px;color:#999999;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong></strong><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">化石湾别墅坐落在世界海岛排名第五的激流岛<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">（WaihekeIsland）</span>。别墅景色出众，设计中处处透露着毛利风格，在激</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\">流岛众多别墅中首屈一指。向外望去，俯瞰豪拉基海湾（Hauraki Gulf）风光，视野开阔，美不胜收。我们的别墅区</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\">不仅有两处旖旎的海滩，还有12英亩的繁茂植被，穿行其间，一面感受轻柔的海风，一面轻嗅清新的空气，惬意自</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\">得。别墅内部设计同样令人眼前一亮，装饰以自然风格和部落风情艺术品，精美别致。室内设有4间卧室和4间浴室，</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\">高品质奢华卧榻、床上用品和卫浴用品让您绝对舒适放心。厨房内设施齐全，储存有新西兰本地食品供您取用。开放</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\">式起居区域空间宽敞，配备了Bose音响系统、天空电视和可供12人就餐的餐桌。一楼设有暖房、影音室、健身房，此</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\">外还另设有一张餐桌可供使用。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/91f03f94-5957-4a13-8cda-f5a2a35df6f5.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/23/b5640ba8-4d96-4ac6-ae31-8fe4a3386b17.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/23/770a4d72-0aa5-4b48-8331-dbc72923c0f5.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/23/4a226308-b6a1-48b4-90ff-1ab37a613b90.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/23/c16181b9-0685-4484-ac13-992fc788d577.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/23/33c03454-177c-4118-8774-f79830fd352e.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/bf65b1bc-de85-4d1d-8c13-44e68d5a4868.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/9e9c9791-6eb2-49d1-8f7e-9b897f6b5486.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/f436c695-96de-42a7-aa4f-b5e1f6602911.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/6cbd7207-342a-4208-ba3c-78eab411c713.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/f975dd8c-b32f-47ac-a7ee-2593c3802c33.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/0ef93d1e-26e6-4185-82ad-66d03e16245c.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img sr