></b></b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"></span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">：5</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">星</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">交通信息：</span></b><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">度假村小岛距仙本那码头45分钟船程（码头距斗湖机场70分钟车程）</span></span>\r\n<hr />\r\n<b><b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">教授语言</span></b><span style=\"color:#999999;\"></span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span></b><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">英语 中文</span> \r\n<hr />\r\n</span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:36px;color:#999999;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong>其它信息</strong></span></span><strong><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Arial, \'Lucida Grande\', \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Hiragino Sans GB W3\', SimSun, STHeiti;font-size:14px;line-height:24px;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-size:12px;font-family:NSimSun;\">卡帕莱是仙本地区设施最好，环境最豪华的水上屋。气氛环境浪漫、优美适合蜜月或者情侣。</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-size:12px;font-family:NSimSun;\">优质的水下世界，适合浮潜和深潜爱好者。四面环海</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-size:12px;font-family:NSimSun;\">随时能欣赏到最美的海景</span></span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;font-size:12px;line-height:24px;color:#64451D;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial, \'Lucida Grande\', \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Hiragino Sans GB W3\', SimSun, STHeiti;font-size:14px;line-height:24px;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">在卡帕莱的一日三餐都是自助餐，游客都会自觉排队取食，卡帕莱所有的食物都是靠每天靠快艇从内陆供给，新鲜并且种类丰富。关掉房间所有的灯，躺在阳台的躺椅上，仰望360度无死角的完美星空，瞬间觉得此刻的宁静是那么的不可思议。</span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;font-size:12px;line-height:24px;color:#64451D;\">与大海零距离接触，</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:12px;line-height:24px;\">这就是水屋的魅力。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/a19c4c28-c72f-4c56-a8e0-33d158801d5f.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/2accf033-3fc2-4640-839d-03d331213dac.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/d6656243-1d4f-4ab1-aea2-6166b06eb370.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/cae5cea3-f821-4492-a890-179bcb0200c7.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/4c199c2d-df82-4144-9d98-0a235039db0e.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/85c9cf6b-cdbd-4db8-af22-8f6da53987e2.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/d9d3922f-2996-4317-8a84-e4c2ec78e26d.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', '1fc35d88-2a75-44ec-9e6c-8ade2f5f941e', '0');
