n> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">教授语言</span></b><span style=\"color:#999999;\"></span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span></b><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">英语、中文</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\"> \r\n<hr />\r\n</span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:36px;color:#999999;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong>其它信息</strong></span></span><span style=\"line-height:36px;color:#999999;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong></strong><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">：</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#003580;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">赤诚和温暖的酒店员工、完备的基本设施、优越的酒店地位、便于游客前往奥费斯岛的各大景点，这些都是众多游客</span><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">选择奥菲斯岛度假村这家酒店的原因。 客人可在无边游泳池畅游，或在Gwandalan Day Spa享受土著风格的独特护</span><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">理，以放松身心。度假酒店设有酒吧以及带户外用餐区的餐厅。房价包含所有由主厨采用地产食材和海鲜烹制的美</span><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">食。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">&nbsp;卧室设计极其舒适，裝修靓丽。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">酒店拥有质量高的综合服务以及完整的基本设施，可满足游客们的所有需</span><span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">求。</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">度</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">假村南距Townsville仅有80公里，是大堡礁（Great Barrier Reef）水域僻静处的世外桃源，距离凯恩斯（Cairns）有</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">1.5小时航程。酒店周围的海洋公园（Marine Park）被列为世界自然遗产，拥有逾1000种热带礁石鱼类，是浮潜和潜</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">水的理想场所。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/46421324-187b-48eb-b155-6a28c2866060.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/4ca993d2-3dc0-41f6-9321-5155136319e4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/0095796c-e9b0-47f3-a6cb-94c0556ac2ba.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"color:#64451D;\"></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/723d6f8a-9551-41e3-8fd4-9db5e5832414.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/9b80187d-987a-4d79-be18-9af8a8704be8.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/5e4c91a2-a73d-419f-8141-31138f970174.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/3c5c1677-3651-4166-8670-d91f20f846f9.j