1D;\">距离安格拉多雷斯巴士站（Angra dos Reis bus terminal）7.7公里</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">教授语言</span></b><span style=\"color:#999999;\"></span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span></b><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">英语、中文</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\"> \r\n<hr />\r\n</span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:36px;color:#999999;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong>其它信息</strong></span></span><span style=\"line-height:36px;color:#999999;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong></strong><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">这家酒店拥有高达60英尺的船只小码头，供享受海水浴的客人使用。这家酒店提供潜水和浮潜课程，但需额外付费。这家酒店离BUS总站只有7.7公里。Pousada Aquamaster Dive Resort酒店提供免费泊车服务，并为带私人快艇的客人设有停放配套设施。离这家酒店只有6公里的老城区提供多间饭店和吧台。酒店每天供应早餐自助，包括热带水果、蛋糕和奶酪。客人可以乘快艇畅游Ilha Grande湾，或者享受在这家酒店修剪整齐的园林漫步的乐趣。所有房间都提供中央空调、电视设施以及带房间家具和床榻的私人房间的阳台。Pousada Aquamaster入住房间光明，放松照明足够，提供当地的裝修摆件。酒店提供能够欣赏海洋全景的室外游泳馆、赠送网络信号连接、潜水和浮潜课程。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/13/cccf18ca-1f69-416d-b628-849337ec5066.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/13/f1810e8c-ca1c-4706-82fa-2c315af52ddc.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/13/9e227106-b879-45c8-9419-b7daad89f789.jpg