color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">圣托里尼首府费拉</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">教授语言</span></b><span style=\"color:#999999;\"></span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span></b><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">英语、中文</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\"> \r\n<hr />\r\n</span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:36px;color:#999999;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong>其它信息</strong></span></span><span style=\"line-height:36px;color:#999999;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong></strong><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">海逸别墅浪漫优雅，既象征着遥远彼岸的想象，又充满着海洋美景的诱惑。<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">优越的地理位置使其成为致敬圣托里尼文化与历史的最佳地点。</span>别墅内存有不乏关于“海”的艺术珍品：</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\">19世纪佚名希腊艺术家创作的系列木炭素描画、19世纪俄罗斯海洋守护神圣尼古拉斯的肖像画以及毕加索所作关于鱼</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\">的瓷画等。希腊罗马式的卫生间铺陈质朴的白色大理石，辅以黑色线条，开阔而厚重，正如海洋。从家具的陈列，到</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\">设备的配置，其每一寸空间的使用都只为满足您的一切需求。即使是最为挑剔的宾客，也将对海逸别墅的精致典雅无</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\">可指摘。<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">如果说雅典残壁存留的是远古的声音，那么圣托里尼就是蓝白相间的极致浪漫所在，在</span><span class=\"15\" style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">圣托里尼骑驴</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">而行，宛若行走在童话之中。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/f7963ab9-b219-493f-8b50-2af8057786c2.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/23/5c67fa66-099e-413e-8531-9d0c9a452a64.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/23/5d8fb5bc-39f7-4860-af1e-45d468c40a98.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/23/76e13d69-095d-40e3-88ca-4d14b3487e42.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/23/56a1dc88-ac88-4253-ab25-18c6a5468796.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/23/9846e890-b7d8-44b3-9f23-e652214ec077.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/23/51fefa02-a631-41db-ad34-758bc17d8165.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"color:#64451D;\"></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/fd8b970d-40f2-425b-8199-f74450371c9a.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/2f0e148e-09b6-40f4-babb-3cf707467ad7.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>', '01768d64-6c80-4f7c-84dc-ce3b26064a1c', '0');
INSERT INTO `dive_store` VALUES ('8f6be2f4-2e5a-488a-a3d4-08e2732d817d', '2016-06-22 15:52:00', '非洲_塞舌尔', 'uploadfiles/store/store_58GL1466582962841.jpg', '塞舌尔-博瓦隆海滩H度假村', '', '', '✈ The H Resort Beau Vallon Beach', '<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:24px;font-family:NSimSun;color:#337FE5;\"><strong><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/22/2e3428e8-77af-43b2-965a-a41d5798d335.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:24px;font-family:NSimSun;color:#337FE5;\"><strong>The H Resort Beau Vallon Beach</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:24px;font-family:NSimSun;color:#337FE5;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;\"></span></span></span></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#333333;\">度假村名称：</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-weight:normal;line-height:1.5;\">博瓦隆海滩H度假村</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#333333;\">地点：</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-weight:normal;line-height:1.5;\">塞舌尔 博瓦隆</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#333333;\">开业时间：</span></strong><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">暂无</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#333333;\">星级：</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-weight:normal;line-height:1.5;\">5星</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#333333;\">交通信息：</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-weight:normal;line-height:1.5;\">距离塞舌尔国际机场30分钟车程</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:24px;font-family:NSimSun;color:#337FE5;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"></span></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#333333;\"></span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#333333;\">教授语言：</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-weight:normal;line-height:1.5;\">英语、中文</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#333333;\">其它信息：</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;\">度假酒店位于马埃岛（Mahé Island），距离贝尔奥伯尔区（Bel Ombre）仅2.6公里，</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1.5;\">设有现代化的Spa中心和众多供</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">应各种美食的餐厅。度假酒店坐落在塞舌尔山国家公园</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">郁郁葱葱的绿色环境中，享有印度洋的美景。度假酒店现代化</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">的套房和别墅均设有室内和室外座椅、空调、平板电视以及沏茶/</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">咖啡设施。别墅还提供私人游泳池、小屋和花洒淋浴</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">设施。每间私人浴室都提供独立的浴缸和淋浴设施。客人可在度</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">假酒店的7间餐厅享用饮品和餐点，同时还可以在</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">度假</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1.5;\">酒店内或周边地区进行打网球、徒步旅行、浮潜和冲浪等各种活动。&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:24px;font-family:NSimSun;color:#337FE5;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"></span></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#333333;\"> </span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><strong><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/22/4e3fd612-df96-46a8-b05b-02713bba9cc7.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/22/20b36ccc-e407-4d93-b9ae-a35df17ff812.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/22/6d8d1a3c-46ed-4e52-a9af-e4408ad0ef7d.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/22/1a127fc6-488c-4cea-bdde-1ccf1ac887a2.jpg\" alt=\"\