:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\">：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">酒店位于热带花园中，俯瞰一个清幽的洞穴，提供带茅草屋顶和当地花岗岩的装饰迷人的住宿。酒店提供一个与大海</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">相连</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">的泳池和一个水疗中心。每间客房均设有一个私人庭院或享有大海或花园景致的阳台。装饰典雅的客房均设有带</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">免费网络</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">连接、无线键盘和客房内电影的等离子电视。客人可以在Elemis Zen Spa水疗中心享用各类美容理疗。酒店</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">还设有一个健</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">身房、蒸汽浴室、小型泳池以及2间带露天淋浴的双人按摩室，提供免费非机动水上体育。并设有一个带</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">泛光灯照明的网</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">球场和带阳伞的室外游泳池。每日提供自助早餐和2间供应自助餐及点菜菜肴的餐厅。享有大海景致的</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">鸡尾酒酒吧设有一</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">个小型图书馆。Beau Vallon Beach海滩和珊瑚礁是浮潜的理想地点。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;\">艾美度假酒店的一流服务带给您无与伦比的入住体验</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/22/00436bb6-491c-46af-b6a1-847c34fbedd9.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/22/90854396-52e2-4fdf-b162-768b7e3759d5.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/22/e1375d8f-2870-4f01-a306-c8b993daea09.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/22/273979d1-c5dd-40bc-b112-3da9aa12b0ee.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/22/26497003-645e-43b1-a250-a4ccef246064.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p styl