rong>其它信息</strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">Laprima Hotel Flores酒店位于</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">Labuan Bajo</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">镇，坐落在</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">Pede</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">海滩上，周围环绕着科莫多国家公园（</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">Komodo National Park Indonesia</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">）的秀美山丘。酒店享有迷人的海景，提供室外游泳池、免费无线网络连接以及舒缓的</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">Spa</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">护理服务。所有空调客房均配备了私人阳台、平面电视和迷你吧。连接浴室提供浴缸或淋浴设施。客人可以沿着白色的沙滩散步，亦可在健身中心锻炼身体或在旅游咨询台安排环岛旅行。酒店还配有商务中心以及</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">24</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">小时随叫随到的医生。酒店内</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">24</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">小时营业的餐厅位于泳池旁，供应当地和国际美食，还提供烈酒、软饮料和小吃菜单</span><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">。\r\n	<hr />\r\n	</span></strong></strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/7dc27c51-3cf0-4819-8cdc-b7bed14b8ab5.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/49e07114-8134-45fd-8e99-0ccda4891bb7.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/f9191d97-9551-470d-828e-170a58057d55.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/338d1