n;line-height:1.5;\">英语、中文</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>其它信息：</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">度假酒店位于Muta海滨，提供6个游泳池、阳光露台、热水浴池、桑拿浴室和健身房。酒店内还设有冒险园、2间餐厅</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">及一个果汁吧，并提供每日自助早餐。客人可以享受攀岩活动，或在酒店的Spa享受按摩服务。度假酒店还提供沙龙、</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">精品店和礼宾服务。La Torre度假酒店色彩缤纷的客房设有私人阳台、电视和迷你吧。部分客房设有拥有游泳池景致</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">和吊床的阳台。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/003709c3-1597-4ce0-a3d7-0348b9558c49.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/daf2a00f-8564-4aab-a24e-c5c59e2f8215.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#337FE5;font-size:24px;\"><strong><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/f0d07a6f-179b-44c8-90c6-a0b44e3bce45.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#337FE5;font-size:24px;\"><strong><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/775256b6-cf9d-4780-9cfc-097acc744cd3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#337FE5;font-size:24px;\"><strong><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/435e7685-2aba-4658-91b0-fa7574cd17fa.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#337FE5;font-size:24px;\"><strong><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/5ce5fa92-ea35-473e-9bb0-de71217c3091.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#337FE5;font-size:24px;\"><strong><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/4b049663-d3db-480e-b239-175ddd9a1ac9.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#337FE5