an></b></b><span style=\"color:#333333;\"></span><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span>：</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">4.5</span></span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">星</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#333333;\">交通信息：</span></b><span style=\"color:#333333;\"></span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">度假村距龙目岛机场需1小时车程</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<b><b><span style=\"color:#333333;\">教授语言</span></b><span style=\"color:#999999;\"></span><span style=\"color:#333333;\">：</span></b><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"><span><span>英语 中文</span> \r\n<hr />\r\n</span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:36px;color:#999999;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#333333;\"><strong>其它信息：</strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:36px;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;\"><span style=\"line-height:19px;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">酒店位置</span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\"> Sekotong Barat</span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">的龙目岛可可提诺斯酒店靠近海湾，住客可方便地前往圣吉吉海滩和</span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">Elak Elak Beach</span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\"></span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">正如名字所说，蓝天碧水，度假村坐落于小山之上，亲近自然，同时坐享海峡绝美景色。</span></span><span style=\"line-height:19px;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">房间宽敞，感觉，舒适，阳台上有躺椅，能够看到大海和泳池的美景。</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">不管是豪华独立套房，蜜月套房或是普通套房，您都可以在此享受到四周环绕的夏日风情。</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">度假村工作人员费尽心思为游客</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">们创造一次温馨且难忘的潜水之旅，同时这也是一个能够满足孩子以及青年们各种活动需求的胜地。</span></span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:36px;color:#999999;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#333333;