ily:NSimSun;\">线网络连接。这栋度假屋设有电视、空调、带微波炉和冰箱的设施齐全的厨房以及带淋浴和吹风机的私人浴室。客人</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">可以在客房内观赏泳池景致。Villas Galapagos Cottages度假屋设有花园、露台以及免费停车场。Villas Galapagos&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">Cottages度假屋距离托尔图加湾（Tortuga Bay）海滩仅有2公里。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/cc505ca9-d7a0-491c-8659-24590b614446.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/c8c6bd22-1be4-4432-8875-a17ae3c6d074.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/2ef49dab-2a88-4830-becd-37e5320788fc.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/8ab6ef7c-17f4-4736-8e0c-88c0f8e4f97b.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/00a41677-9b90-4e1b-b085-7b5530d78bb4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/6f11831d-a871-48ef-8618-7da267ca6336.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/619aac72-fb20-444e-923a-5086f117ce0e.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/7e7685e7-b384-4b92-a849-f6b8e60c4225.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>', '01768d64-6c80-4f7c-84dc-ce3b26064a1c', '0');
INSERT INTO `dive_store` VALUES ('c1d4bea4-6c6c-47a7-955f-fb4ac3c94c38', '2016-06-21 10:08:11', '非洲_塞舌尔', 'uploadfiles/store/store_D4tj1466485745439.jpg', '塞舌尔-四季酒店', '', '', '✈ Four Seasons Resort', '<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;font-family:NSimSun;color:#337FE5;\"><strong><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/21/30f95131-96ac-4324-b35d-6a5738c5f0a0.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;font-family:NSimSun;color:#337FE5;\"><strong>Four Seasons Resort</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;font-family:NSimSun;color:#337FE5;\"><strong></strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\"><strong>度假村名称：</strong><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">四季酒店</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>地点：</strong><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\">塞舌尔 马埃岛贝拉扎尔区</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>开业时间：</strong><span>2009年</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>星级：</strong><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">5星</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>交通信息：</strong><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">距离塞舌尔国家机场30分钟车程</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>教授语言：</strong><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">英语、中文</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>其它信息：</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;\">酒店位于Baie Lazare地区的Petite Anse区，距离沙滩不足5米，拥有Spa、健身中心、游泳池和水上运动馆。每座空调</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1.5;\">别墅都包含私人游泳池和露台。房间配有卫星电视、迷你吧和沏茶/咖啡设施。浴室提供淋浴、免费洗浴用品、浴袍和</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1.5;\">拖鞋。Kannel餐厅提供国际美食午餐以及亚洲和克里奥尔美食晚餐。ZEZ餐厅供应每日特色菜和点菜国际早餐，并提供</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1.5;\">现代地中海风味的美食晚餐。Kannel酒吧全天供应小吃、果汁饮料和鸡尾酒，而ZEZ酒廊供应鸡尾酒、葡萄酒、新鲜寿</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1.5;\">司和生鱼片。免费的儿童活动可让小朋友们度过愉快时光。这家度假酒店还可安排浮潜、风帆冲浪、钓鱼、直升机之</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1.5;\">旅和骑自行车等活动。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/21/feede235-18ce-47de-877a-4f3b65221047.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\"><strong><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/21/a7c12ebb-5bdc-4461-88ea-67c9b4f064ea.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\"><strong><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/21/92666ec6-bb9d-47e4-b91e-46c5c3e2ec3f.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\"><strong><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/21/6d4c75d2-9e9b-4ac9-9c02-714ee14b76db.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\"><strong><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/21/bf566862-d5c2-48f5-99a0-48b2b8896afb.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\"><strong><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/21/e59b55cb-d521-42ec-b2b4-59c72d23b371.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\"><strong><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/21/1e081595-139a-4822-9ce9-1a235b659b98.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\"><strong><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/21/36b5a14f-b62f-4a1f-b94a-a512365631bd.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\"><strong><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/21/3c6516a3-fe5d-40b2-b918-f6fe170c6610.jpg\" a