451D;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:12px;\">：</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#999999;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;\"> </span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"background:white;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#64451D;\">诗巴丹岛马布度假村坐落在马布岛南部一角，俯瞰西巴丹岛。建材采用婆罗洲原生材料，外形别致新颖。水屋有</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">45</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">间，其中</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">22</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">间是独立水屋和</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">23</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">间半独立的两房水屋。最多可容纳</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">90</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">客人同时入住。所有的别墅都有隔蚊帘，热水淋浴设施，空调，独立浴室。度假村拥有测量与深</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">6</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">英尺年底</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">41</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">英尺×</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">21</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">英尺乙烯基游泳池，和一个</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">4-6</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">人的按摩漩涡水疗。还有一个大型的宴会厅和酒吧区，每天的膳食都由厨师精心烹饪，餐厅内还有天然果汁，椰子水，葡萄酒和含酒精饮品提供。度假村还设有一个小型购物店，出售</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">T</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">恤衫，电池，洗漱用品和纪念品等。</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/638af4ba-a718-4edf-b19c-c134690f9484.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/04/29/ecd56981-51f5-44ec-b262-870fec280761.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/04/29/c787509e-be5a-42e0-b655-098330959803.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/04/29/9fdf3c39-3814-4006-a654-05859f6105a7.jpg\" alt=\"\"