><span style=\"color:#999999;\"></span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-size:12px;\">：</span></b><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">英语 中文</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"><span> \r\n<hr />\r\n</span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:36px;color:#999999;font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#333333;font-size:12px;\"><strong>其它信息</strong></span></span><span style=\"line-height:36px;color:#999999;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#333333;\"><strong></strong><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-size:12px;\">：</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1.5;\">Huma Island Resort and Spa酒店被清澈碧绿的海水所环绕，是一家度假式生活与时尚舒适生活兼得的酒店。</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">酒店设有豪华的茅草屋顶别墅，拥有高高的竹子天花板和私人日光浴平台，享有蔚蓝太平洋（Pacific）的全方位美景。酒店的起居区配备了现代家具，宽敞的浴室设有独立淋浴和卫生间。客人甚至可以在露天热水浴池欣赏日出或日落美景。</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1.5;\">酒店内的Kapuruan Spa中心拥有独特的玻璃地板建筑设计，客人可以边享受spa护理边欣赏清澈水景，此处提供各种亚洲spa护理，还设有一间极具异国情调的放松土耳其浴室。</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1.5;\">酒店内设有7个餐饮场所，满足客人的味蕾。客人可以在Rudi\'s Wine and Cheese Bar葡萄酒和奶酪吧品尝葡萄酒和奶酪；在Al Fairuz餐厅享用美</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1.5;\">味的黎巴嫩美食，或者在Al Dente意大利餐厅享受水上用餐体验。众多餐饮选择必将满足每位客人的口味。\r\n	<hr />\r\n	</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#003580;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/a58a5df7-