ont-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:Helvetica;color:#64451D;\">感到激动和满足。每天早上推开房门，看见的是天堂般的美景，更别提若是游艇赛季到来，这里将汇集全世界最奢侈</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:Helvetica;color:#64451D;\">的游艇的奢华场景。想必对于游艇爱好者来说，此处不来，真是一大遗憾吧？</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">游艇俱乐部别墅是豪华的海滨别墅，毗</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">邻汉密尔顿岛游艇俱乐部。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">•坐拥丹特水道壮丽令人屏息的海景</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">•由</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">澳大利亚著名建筑师Walter Barda设计</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">•适合家庭入住，</span>特别注重私密性和空间</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">•游艇、高尔夫</span>、泳池、海滩、美景......丰富多彩的活动在等着您</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/c54aff94-7aab-4866-bf00-2a0d9291cc4b.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/24/edde4643-7b79-41fc-a160-955915839c6e.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/3001e65a-322f-487e-be70-a4bc6be076fd.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/24/69e4b943-8b8b-4ae7-acc5-638b1c95b2b3.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/24/06e4ed19-3a9b-4be5-9d6b-76ca56c49f67.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/24/4cab1e0c-456c-4c04-a82e-5cd27e0a6d4e.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/1edf4e24-5931-40c4-84c3-7ee2fd89d7d6.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/a07e68c2-bc80-45d2-b531-cc6058642d8b.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/c2cf4b09-bd39-432e-94b8-330bc9747ca3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/08/f16cd0a3-4f5b-4298-9717-aa6cbfefc5a6.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/24/5dfb9545-e50e-4b9b-97a9-6798d8ed7449.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>', '01768d64-6c80-4f7c-84dc-ce3b26064a1c', '0');
