ine-height:19.6px;\">Eleftherios Venizelos International Airport国际机场2小时车程</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">教授语言</span></b><span style=\"color:#999999;\"></span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span></b><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">英语、中文</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\"> \r\n<hr />\r\n</span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:36px;color:#999999;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong>其它信息</strong></span></span><span style=\"line-height:36px;color:#999999;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong></strong><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">Grand Bleu酒店的每间空调客房都设有私人阳台，并配有电视和带有吹风机的浴室。所有客房都享有大海、游泳池或</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">者园景花园的景色。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">主餐厅供应自助餐。包括当地葡萄酒。海滩旁的Thalassa Tavern餐厅供应希腊特色菜。主酒吧、</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">Thalassa池畔酒吧或者Zorba海滩酒吧供应饮品。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">Grand Bleu Hotel酒店拥有一个沙滩排球场和篮球场。酒店还提供烹</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">饪和陶器制作课程。沙滩上提供水上运动，酒店每周还组织徒步旅行和骑自行车游览。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">Grand Bleu酒店距离Eretria仅</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\">2公里。酒店接待处提供汽车租赁服</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\">务，并提供免费停车场。&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/d2956f42-01e0-455c-ac5e-54c23b6943cd.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/19/a50ffa76-d822-4284-ad58-36dc0fb81ec7.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/19/ab2899f2-1a12-45d2-810d-0d69533f7a62.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/38c02062-c376-420e-a92e-9b6690503f5d.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/19/705e4a56-aa63-4711-9413-2493b731860b.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/f0b99742-ec3a-488a-9dc3-b2f564cbdce3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/0c9043f7-c5a0-4dba-b8ca-55707589f63f.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/18615d7d-1617-444d-b824-8e48c40182cd.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/19/189f4d64-5fd8-4cf1-9c65-1f7c4150991d.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/277e6095-a7ac-4417-9f04-6a5907f5c61f.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/aa556a47-d09a-400e-9ec9-f634ef74ed14.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>', '01768d64-6c80-4f7c-84dc-ce3b26064a1c', '0');
INSERT INTO `dive_store` VALUES ('d36d49fb-8f85-446b-a76f-2ab8c793bf5a', '2016-04-26 10:35:28', '亚洲_日本_冲绳', 'uploadfiles/store/store_g7X21465967530044.jpg', '日本 冲绳-布森纳露台俱乐部疗养度假村酒店', '', '', '✈  The Terrace Club Wellness Resort at Busena', '<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#337FE5;font-family:NSimSun;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/ab59df83-f9b3-4d37-b880-4a800bf3e790.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#337FE5;font-family:NSimSun;\">The Terrace Club Wellness Resort at Busena</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:12px;\"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:12px;\"><strong>度假村名称：</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;\"></span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:NSimSun;\">布森纳露台俱乐部疗养度假村酒店</span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\"><strong>地点：</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">日本 冲绳</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\"><strong>开业时间：</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">暂无</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\"><strong>星级</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\"><strong>：</strong>5</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">星</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\"><strong>交通信息：</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">度假酒店距离那霸机场</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">47</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">公里车程</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\"><strong>教授语言：</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">英语 中文 日文</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">其它信息：</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">The Terrace Club Wellness Resort at Busena</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:NSimSun;\">酒店位于名护（Nago），设有spa中心、私人海滩区、季节性的室外游泳池、阳光露台、餐厅、酒吧以及免费的内部私人停车场。为方便客人，部分客房设有休息区。每间客房均提供咖啡机以及带浴缸、坐浴盆、浴袍、拖鞋和免费洗浴用品的私人浴室。Terrace Club酒店提供免费WiFi。客房还提供平板电视以及DVD播放机。酒店提供免费班车服务和礼品店。The Terrace Club\r\nWellness Resort at Busena酒店距离Busena Marine Park海洋公园600米，距离万国津梁馆（Bankoku Shinryokan）700米漂亮的景观，简直在天堂般，没有吵杂声，只有虫鸣鸟叫海浪声，下午还有免费酒精饮料无限畅饮时间，搭配最美味的烟燻火腿、起士、水果。游泳池的水很软很清澈，海水很透澈还不时看到鱼群跳要水面。这里具有船潜设备，上面的设施一应俱全。晒着太阳，简直是人间天堂！</span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/aefdda58-aee3-4a0f-92ba-c074c6ea7a4f.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/661a1816-041e-4a88-bf13-7390beef3f26.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/dde89caa-e7b5-40fd-a8a2-18b3f28d4d76.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/bf1c39ac-aad0-432e-bd0a-d3fdcda02302.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/b5e72242-ab74-4dee-9e63-731d6da7f24b.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/da6a9a7c-cecf-4546-af8e-a9c1221de74a.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/5ca61511-57c3-4de8-bc18-a05816f5e668.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/ac2e83de-6263-4e19-90b1-e2d84b7dceff.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/0c49fc8a-c4d3-4e6f-b65b-39b6c100b4fa.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/23b2d49d-674a-454a-ab03-3c13f399d1d0.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/fbeb44bb-07f5-48b7-9344-fa81fa867051.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/d68156d0-d03d-4c22-93bd-e56d837be558.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/53414c7d-b6e1-4f7d-a9af-65c85f6fa4a3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>', '1fc35d88-2a75-44ec-9e6c-8ade2f5f941e', '0');
