塔内格拉海滩（Ponta Negra Beach）的白色沙滩上，设有14个游泳池、5间餐厅、</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">1间spa、1间高科技健身房以及观景阳台。宽敞而明亮的客房均装饰有欢快的色彩和当地的艺术品，设有空调、液晶有</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">线电视、电话和迷你吧。部分客房享有海景，部分客房享有沙丘景致。Ocean Palace Beach Resort &amp; Bungalows酒店的客人可在周围环绕着热带植物的热水浴池内放松身心，或享受桑拿浴和按摩服务，还可参加普拉提课程以锻炼身</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">体。酒店还设有儿童俱乐部。酒店提供的餐饮场所包括专门供应地道巴西招牌菜的Brazilian restaurant餐厅。Le&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">Solei餐厅供应当地美食。Sunrise餐厅供应丰盛的自助早餐。酒店还设有寿司吧和比萨饼店。度假酒店设有免费私</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">人停车场，对面即是纳塔尔会议中心（Natal Convention Centre）。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/cb7f1c76-4f6c-47ea-90ee-dd7ba25f94d2.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/90a42e4f-680d-47b1-8563-2d4c1e3a088f.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/e8824823-6dbf-471a-bcc9-0275ac2cb868.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/f010dbcc-79dd-412f-9deb-4bb5d0590fe5.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/c79474ec-9287-49fc-a870-10eef87fe733.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/6136612f-f427-45a0-ac54-7d37d9aa9611.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/a11e64f7-e336-4023-810f-b5abf4654312.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/a790446d-5bab-40a0-9f2c-55443e9d070e.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/e17d19d6-f834-4cd1-8393-47a13fb7a672.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/73d1f849-ae43-4585-9fa6-02f9603a4444.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/620d5c93-78b4-4f4a-b8a4-b75f1eda6da8.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/29bd3195-0507-4335-9973-1f05ae7f0e21.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/54f34754-c680-4fd5-bb1e-2f2f16791f30.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/24/a9b2d462-fb1d-4df1-8538-27aa44c6439e.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>', '01768d64-6c80-4f7c-84dc-ce3b26064a1c', '0');
INSERT INTO `dive_store` VALUES ('f660daf6-1f96-42bc-9ced-485b2e994442', '2016-05-23 16:38:27', '大洋洲_新西兰', 'uploadfiles/store/store_R3QL1465697559738.jpg', '新西兰-船屋别墅', '', '', '✈Boat Villa', '<h1 class=\"item\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span><span style=\"font-size:32px;line-height:48px;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/23/a02f7fbb-c1b9-4b72-a6a1-7319930efd20.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</h1>\r\n<h1 class=\"item\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#337FE5;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"line-height:48px;color:#337FE5;font-family:NSimSun;\">Boat Villa</span></span> \r\n</h1>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:36px;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:36px;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">度假村名称：</span></strong></span></span><span style=\"line-height:36px;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';line-height:1;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">船屋别墅</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\"></span></span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">地点：</span></strong><span style=\"color:#333333;\"></span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">新西兰 群岛湾 特提</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">开业时间</span></b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"></span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">：暂无</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">星级：</span></b></b><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">5</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">星</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">交通信息：</span></b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"></span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">距离岛屿湾机场（Bay of Island Airport）约45分钟车程</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><b><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">教授语言</span></b><span style=\"color:#999999;\"></span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span></b><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">英语、中文</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\"> \r\n<hr />\r\n</span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:36px;color:#999999;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong>其它信息</strong></span></span><span style=\"line-height:36px;color:#999999;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong></strong><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">船屋别墅位于新西兰群岛湾（Bay of Islands），建筑豪华，环境优美，海滩和农田遥相呼应，丛林间又是野生动物</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\">的乐园，一派生机盎然的美妙画面。船屋别墅在原先建筑结构的基础上大胆地采用了开放式设计，在室外娱乐区便能</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\">感受到怀罗阿海湾（Wairoa Bay）清凉宜人的海水，而走近室内，设计清新自然，装修精湛雅致，采用天然石材与木</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\">材，舒适宜居。室内包括一间主卧室、一间双人间和一间豪华的浴室。夜幕降临，四下静谧安逸，同亲朋来到室外炉</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\">火旁围坐，或静静小憩，或畅谈忘忧，也可以一起烧烤，充分享受在船屋别墅中度假的自由自在。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/23/bde2d396-6862-4232-8a7c-74446c0d34ec.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/23/59227c88-73ac-4bf7-817f-f37d11faf71f.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/23/367017c5-446b-4348-940c-1b161b11acd6.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/23/334ec38f-9364-40bb-8bd3-5705062e98e4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/23/48883dd9-f912-4e88-bed1-aae8f7ed854a.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/23/ee34de87-11f3-425b-97c3-a49d3d44b8fc.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/23/3fa749ae-5842-4c6e-bd91-7ce6f13a3e22.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/352da03d-1471-4443-8370-cdc31d17ca6e.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/f7a426cc-ef62-4177-b19e-bf81044aed1d.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/12/8c7a524a-e0f8-4dbd-a0f2-6fa44a229472.jpg\" alt=\"\"