场需50分钟机程</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"font-size:13.3333px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#337FE5;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><strong></strong></span><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><strong>教授语言：</strong><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">英语、中文</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"font-size:13.3333px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\"><strong>其它信息：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;background-color:white;\"> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;color:#64451D;\">J<span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">umeirah Dhevanafushi</span></span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">度假村提供入住别墅的豪华享受，步行可及清澈的泻湖水域和海滩，拥有私人游泳池、一流的水疗中心、免费无线网络连接和</span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">4</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">个餐饮场所。度假村的独立别墅享有高质量的木质家具，室内设施包括</span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">IPod</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">基座、平板电视等的现代科技设施。慵懒的午后，可在室外休息区放松身心。度假村提供钓鱼、潜水和帆船等多种水上活动设施。此外，水疗中心还设有舒适的按摩和桑拿设施。</span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">Azara</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">餐厅供应多种国际美食，为您带来美好的一天。</span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">Mumayaz</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">餐厅给您带来星空下用餐的绝佳体验。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/5e7eb2d5-8d90-4409-a8d6-b47ac9c8aabe.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/06/15/ca5f2ef9-e382-4246-aa85-92aab3ed2ddf.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/0