ight:1;font-family:NSimSun;\"></span><span style=\"line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">图巴塔哈、维萨亚斯群岛</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#333333;line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;\">舱位数量：</span></span></strong></span></strong><span style=\"line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;line-height:1;\"></span></span><span style=\"line-height:1;\"><span style=\"color:#999999;line-height:1;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"></span><span style=\"line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">8</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#E56600;\"><span style=\"color:#999999;line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"color:#333333;line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;\">可容纳客人：</span></span></strong></span><span style=\"line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\"></span></span></span></strong><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#E56600;\"><span style=\"color:#999999;line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"></span><span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;\">16位</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;\">其他信息：</span></span></strong></span></strong><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"line-height:30px;font-size:14px;color:#64451D;\">海德门号是一艘经济舒适性价比较好的专业潜水游轮，长25米，船长Pierlo。船上有空调沙龙室，设有座椅休闲区，相机充电处，纯平电视，音响，图书角，音乐碟和大量的电影可供旅客在潜水之余放松休闲。餐厅位于室外（有遮阳篷），配有酒水吧台，音乐系统。拥有潜水甲板，并设有清洗水箱，相机充电处和潜水服晒晾处。顶层甲板设有阳光躺椅。为潜数少于30潜的新潜水员提供私人潜水导向服务，价格为6美金/人/潜。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/02/18/985e520b-8622-4b49-9418-b6762b6961ec.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/02/18/b15484cc-dade-48fc-a213-1f18e553a552.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"></span><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/02/18/60165904-8ee5-4684-9e36-ef20c1d9eb62.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/02/18/49a29924-7d3f-447b-8104-8146a35dd933.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/02/18/fcc7d8e5-d995-4ff2-b295-e7e9aa59cc97.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/02/18/121a52ed-4783-4d49-86cb-80afee60a9e8.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/02/18/72165731-ad19-43c1-baf3-4363fb4c1ff1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/02/18/04b6df65-554d-4eb7-9107-1eeaf6d2ead6.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/02/18/21270f61-34a5-4810-9d07-5c1e8badbee8.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>', null, 'uploadfiles/travel/travel_m5HV1455785411725.jpg', '海德门号', null, '', '| Seadoors', '1fc35d88-2a75-44ec-9e6c-8ade2f5f941e', '菲律宾图巴塔哈群礁、米沙鄢群岛', '', '菲律宾', '', 'Seadoors', '0');
