#64451D;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">科隆&amp;阿波礁，图巴塔哈，维萨亚斯群岛</span></span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#333333;line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;\">舱位数量</span><span style=\"line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;line-height:1;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#333333;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\">：</span></span></strong></span></span></strong><span style=\"color:#333333;line-height:1;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"></span><span style=\"line-height:1;\"><span style=\"color:#999999;line-height:1;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"></span><span style=\"line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">8</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#E56600;\"><span style=\"color:#999999;line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"color:#333333;line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;\">可容纳客人</span><span style=\"line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#333333;\"><span style=\"line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;color:#333333;\">：</span></span></strong></span></span></span></strong><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#E56600;\"><span style=\"color:#999999;line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"></span><span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;\">16位</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1;\">其它信息<strong><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span></span></strong></span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">Atlantis Azores是一艘非常舒适的潜水游轮，一直以来提供优质服务。旅客在沙龙室可观看电影，在图书角阅读书籍，玩游戏等。船上的阳光甲板平台配有舒适休闲室，小酒吧，热水浴缸，休闲座椅区，以及冲晾处等贴心设施。晚上，船员会进行演讲，游客可以摄影、浮潜以及加入陆上游览项目。游客可在船上买到当地特产，明信片等。所有潜水员有各自的储物空间，有3个相机工作台和1个相机充电站，冷热水冲凉处，还提供髙氧气瓶服务。</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\">另外，</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1.5;\">Atlantis Azores的餐厅被誉为“菲律宾最好的游轮餐厅”！船员使用语言为英语！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/02/18/05064dba-04e1-489d-8c2d-244b5d54d726.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/02/18/d4754a85-3b61-469e-aba5-0251f76bca68.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/02/18/b5216791-932f-4c90-a773-008349ac58f7.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/02/18/af229339-9010-4040-9009-0fd570a6ab42.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/02/18/a1081aad-d416-4fcd-946e-aaa51e0c2a00.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/02/18/741271e5-3548-400e-ade2-617b2b30208a.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/02/18/5f04afeb-a80e-4f50-bde7-ec23ff4857a8.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/02/18/eb12f1d4-a49a-4dee-b1df-274247a12832.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/02/18/d138041b-0baa-4546-8888-39586eee2e7a.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"></span> \r\n</p>', null, 'uploadfiles/travel/travel_wqbC1455779558410.jpg', '亚特兰蒂斯号', null, '', '| Atlantis Azores', '1fc35d88-2a75-44ec-9e6c-8ade2f5f941e', '菲律宾图巴塔哈群岛、薄荷岛/米沙鄢群岛', '', '菲律宾', '', 'Atlantis Azores', '0');
