3333;line-height:1;\">舱位数量</span><span style=\"line-height:1;\"><span style=\"color:#999999;line-height:1;\">：</span></span></strong><span style=\"color:#333333;line-height:1;\"></span><span style=\"line-height:1;\"><span style=\"color:#999999;line-height:1;\"></span><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">13</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#E56600;\"><span style=\"color:#999999;line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;line-height:1;\">可容纳客人</span><span style=\"line-height:1;\">:</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"color:#E56600;\"><span style=\"color:#999999;line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;line-height:1;\"></span><span style=\"line-height:1;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">25</span></span></span></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#E56600;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1;\">位</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#333333;line-height:1;\">其它信息:</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-size:14px;\">Nautilus Explorer号是一艘美丽豪华的潜水游轮，提供一流的服务品质，该游轮主要提供来往于墨西哥</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-size:14px;\"></span><span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:12px;font-size:14px;\">索科罗群岛与瓜达卢佩岛</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:12px;\"></span><span style=\"color:#64451D;font-size:14px;\">的潜水之旅；船上基础设施齐全，还配有一个露天按摩浴缸；每个房间设有中央空调、书桌、私人卫生浴室等，餐厅主要提供北美、欧洲及当地墨西哥菜肴，也可以根据特殊旅客提供正规严格的犹太餐、穆斯林食等！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/01/21/a826a0d1-8e11-4e24-9509-256389b87dba.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/01/21/41c59fdf-b1d8-4fc6-845a-e05f91d79e9b.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\