\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#333333;\">其它信息</span></b><b><span style=\"color:#333333;\">:</span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#333333;\"></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1.5;\">游轮MV Nautilus Explorer目的地为索科罗群岛，瓜达卢佩岛，它是一艘长35米，宽8.5专为潜水爱好者们制造的一艘豪华游轮。可一次性容纳24位乘客，提供墨西哥风情的食物，甲板上提供带有空调的沙龙室，沙龙室设有台球桌，电视机，以及酒水吧台等一系列的娱乐休闲设施。船长是经营多年的好手，游玩的游客可以一边享受阳光美食，一边可以潜入水中，与水下生物进行亲密接触。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/12/1a1e4be5-e21f-4cb5-a53b-1add7b925c8c.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/12/7480e126-9750-4d9d-a754-a2dc54b9bccb.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/12/708af60c-2e4f-4f2f-81cc-fe04163bd8fe.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/12/e2520d24-17a0-49fc-b0fc-3697be0271dd.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/12/2e0bdeff-595e-4f3a-9762-ef4675103af4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/12/0c163ca8-a0d9-4887-bfde-efaea3b33dac.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/12/966eede5-9e0a-4da3-86e5-e28b465aec8a.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/12/0e046c44-ee6a-457c-b6e9-a263be5014ee.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>', null, 'uploadfiles/travel/travel_rpa61463020016656.jpg', 'MV 鹦螺探险号', null, '', '| MV Nautilus Explorer',