line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:12px;\">22</span> \r\n<hr />\r\n<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#000000;font-size:12px;\"><strong>其它信息：</strong></span></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-size:14px;\">又名EL Princess Ushwa，船长32.5米，宽10米；拥有共11间豪华房间，干净舒适！专业供电系统24小时无间断运行，电压220伏特；</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#64451D;font-size:14px;\">客舱均配备独立的冲淋卫生间和空调系统，带三层甲板及阳光甲板，游艇大厅配备wifi！<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;line-height:21px;\">上层甲板是主控舰桥、露天阳光甲板，有<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;line-height:21px;\">船长休息舱以及2两间奢华双人高级客舱。</span></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#64451D;font-size:14px;\">下层甲板分布有8个</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\">高级客舱，主甲板有一间Superior套房，酒吧，厨房，露天及室内用餐区，同时拥有电视，音乐，wifi和电脑的尊享休闲区</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"http://www.e-diving.com.cn/attached/image/2015/11/15/c5648ff4-900b-42b6-9362-989917100f12.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2015/11/15/e162d145-515a-4197-9894-6b8149f6db86.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2015/11/15/0f6fd3ab-6772-4152-b90e-cb87384aec9a.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2015/11/15/8f2e7e2d-c6e4-4a9d-b096-a7f5bd488f77.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2015/11/15/6d9960f3-3216-4873-a975-442c87af0a31.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>', null, 'uploadfiles/travel/travel_MQk01447565661309.jpg', '蓝军2号', '19500', 'ST01', '|  又名EL Princess Ushwa', '6a040c09-5758-41f8-8910-bf556692e824', '马尔代夫', 'Male', '马尔代夫', 'Maldives', 'Blue Force Two', '0');
INSERT INTO `dive_travel` VALUES ('4c4e958c-3887-4d96-b321-7ff4297a2eb9', '2016-05-10 14:24:27', '<h1 style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1;color:#337FE5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/10/3b65df3e-a85b-48a6-8bf4-ad8a52b17a09.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</h1>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1;color:#000000;\">Okeanos Aggressor</span><br />\r\n</h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:24px;color:#337FE5;\"><b>凯诺斯侵略者号</b></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:24px;\"><b><br />\r\n</b></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#333333;\">船名：</span></b><span style=\"color:#333333;\"></span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">凯诺斯侵略者号</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<hr />\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#333333;\">船体：</span></b><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">双层</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<hr />\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#333333;\">目的地</span></b><b><strong><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">：</span></strong></b><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">可可岛</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<hr />\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#333333;\">舱位数量</span></b><b><span style=\"color:#333333;\">：</span></b><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">8</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<hr />\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#333333;\">可容纳客人</span></b><span style=\"color:#333333;\">:</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">&nbsp;22</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;\">位</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<hr />\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#333333;\">其它信息</span></b><b><span style=\"color:#333333;\">:</span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">游轮Okeanos Aggressor 是一艘长110英尺的游轮，可同时接纳22位旅客出游，船上共有9间豪华双人客舱（其中4间双床客舱－均为单人床，5间上下床客舱－上床为单人床，下床为双人床）和1间四人客舱（宿舍制客舱，4张单人床），所有客舱都配有私人卫浴室，空调系统，电视，DVD播放器，和储物空间。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;\">游轮Okeanos Aggressor拥有一间大型沙龙室，带有影音中心和用餐区；一个长为英尺40阳光甲板配有休闲区和躺椅；酒吧吧台；一间相片工作中心，还有一个贵重物品储藏室，可为旅客储藏护照，现金，信用卡等贵重物品。船上可通过卫星通讯系统收发邮电，但使用此服务会有额外的收费。另外，船上还有专为旅客准备用来储藏潜水装备的储物空间，且每人都有独立的锁。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#555555;font-family:\'Lucida Sans\', \'Lucida Grande\', \'Trebuchet MS\', Tahoma, Arial, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Geneva, Lucida, sans-serif;font-size:13.76px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-size:13.76px;line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/10/314c0713-b40f-4bef-b8f9-37ef474ec31e.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#555555;font-family:\'Lucida Sans\', \'Lucida Grande\', \'Trebuchet MS\', Tahoma, Arial, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Geneva, Lucida, sans-serif;font-size:13.76px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-size:13.76px;line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/10/c395c15e-7cd8-49bd-a8c3-e00ecc432e15.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#555555;font-family:\'Lucida Sans\', \'Lucida Grande\', \'Trebuchet MS\', Tahoma, Arial, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Geneva, Lucida, sans-serif;font-size:13.76px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-size:13.76px;line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/10/5588