8</span><span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1.5;font-family:NSimSun;\">位</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<hr />\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#333333;\">其它信息</span></b><b><span style=\"color:#333333;\">:</span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-size:12px;\">游轮Tropic Dancer带领着无数潜水爱好者们前往帕劳群岛的各个潜点探奇，其中包含著名的蓝角。游轮简洁大方，宽敞舒适的设计加上专业的潜水设施，将令所有潜水员们都有如家一般的亲切感。船上共有9间客舱：8间豪华客舱，配有：一张上下床（上铺为单人床，下铺为双人床)，私人卫浴室，空调，观景窗，吹风机等。和1间位于潜水甲板的标准客舱，配有：一张上下床（上铺为单人床，下铺为双人床)，私人卫浴室，空调，吹风机等。所有客舱都有储物柜和充足的储物空间便于旅客储藏行李。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/11/836255b7-6b59-459e-b4c7-49c9e23b2269.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/11/a31ea62c-a3c1-476f-99ad-fd93103d0f18.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-size:12px;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/11/32fe43a3-5dda-4720-a4b6-4a0b880ce6d3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-size:12px;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/11/a694764c-78c2-4f97-b921-10f55c22f586.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-size:12px;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/11/1e53d4e6-e13a-43f5-9afa-a44662e9feeb.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-size:12px;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/11/8f4f3655-219e-4882-9534-93be66961250.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-size:12px;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/05/11/ccf17335-d7f2-4f06-b7f2-e0e6b6a3d9c4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	