oft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"color:#333333;line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;\">目的地</span><span style=\"line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span>：</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"color:#333333;line-height:1;\"></span><span style=\"line-height:1;\"><span></span><span style=\"color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\">埃及红海</span></span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#333333;line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;\">舱位数量</span><span style=\"line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"color:#999999;line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;\">：</span></span></strong><span style=\"color:#333333;line-height:1;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"></span><span style=\"line-height:1;\"><span style=\"color:#999999;line-height:1;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"></span><span style=\"line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;color:#64451D;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">12</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#E56600;\"><span style=\"color:#999999;line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"color:#333333;line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;\">可容纳客人</span><span style=\"line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;\">:</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"color:#E56600;\"><span style=\"color:#999999;line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"color:#333333;line-height:1;\"></span><span style=\"line-height:1;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\">24</span></span></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-family:NSimSun;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;line-height:1;font-family:NSimSun;\">位</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:1;\">其它信息:</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#64451D;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">C-埃科尔号是一艘非常舒适的高档次潜水游轮，由法国顶级船宿运营公司代理经营常年在红海及境内提供高品质潜水之旅。该船身长34米、宽8米，属于木质结构！船上配有各种娱乐设施：休闲区、影音播放区、电视DVD等；餐厅主要提供自助餐服务：以西餐和当地埃及美食为主！船上使用英语及法语！每间房间配有空调系统、电视、小吧台及私人卫生浴，加上船员们周到贴心的服务，让你的潜水旅行舒适又惬意！</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/01/21/976f1a45-4f7f-4c09-b8e7-c086c349e51e.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/01/21/bfd76334-f3d5-45c0-b26c-dfa662927b79.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/01/21/fb238032-0fe5-44b5-8b1e-730470965707.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/01/21/a95a5e70-3d7b-4654-bbc5-4991482d0008.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/01/21/d766252f-c3f3-4ab0-858c-cf43d034c3a5.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/01/21/c8cf6282-0ade-4508-b808-8dd27d88720c.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/01/21/42edafd3-8bce-4da8-9972-ac1363875fda.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/01/21/a8f0e54d-3dc6-427d-9c77-e94fe872c982.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>', null, 'uploadfiles/travel/travel_frDc1453387523824.jpg', 'C-埃科尔号', null, '', '|  C-Echol', '1fc35d88-2a75-44ec-9e6c-8ade2f5f941e', '红海', '', '埃及', '', 'C-Echol', '0');
