4451D;font-size:14px;\">船上设有</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-size:14px;\">令人惊叹的全海景甲板酒吧以及室外的餐厅（当然你也可以选择坐在室内），你可以在舒适的座位上放松放松,看看世界,同时细品一杯冰镇的鸡尾酒并享受一个微微徐风的日落时光。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-size:14px;\">在休息区域里甚至拥有连网的图书馆，挂壁电视机，DVD，WII和音乐设备。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-size:14px;\">客舱的房间非常宽敞，房间内有最好的柚木内饰和最新的设施，提供24小时冷热水。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;color:#64451D;font-size:14px;\">船上拥有最新的GPS和国际直拨电话、传真和电子邮件服务！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/01/22/b32916eb-0f05-4a72-b50d-404232f46f81.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/attached/image/2016/01/22/fafcf62c-f913-4a3a-a4ac-7e017dde7de6.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2016/01/22/b6521d2a-f3bb-4d7f-91d9-74d11af6f000.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2015/10/22/8a866fe2-1e04-45ce-8ad1-05f623a884a4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2015/10/22/94471a05-b864-42a8-9c3a-ca4ac7392246.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2015/10/22/598e6291-460b-40da-9454-644034609cff.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2015/10/22/0d65c679-1d02-442c-8f17-8e9eaf10e3da.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img src=\"/attached/image/2015/11/15/b5ed8927-6958-404f-a0da-5b3f27521620.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>', null, 'uploadfiles/travel/travel_Ddx71446820808370.jpg', '捕梦者Ⅱ号', '11160', 'ST01', '|  Dream Catcher Ⅱ', '6a040c09-5758-41f8-8910-bf556692e824', '马尔代夫', 'Male', '马尔代夫', 'Maldives', 'Dream Catcher Ⅱ', '3');
